And this as the helper:

```
def compute_partial_header_hash(
    previous_partial_header_hash: Hash32,
    parent_block_hash: Hash32,
    parent_requests_hash: Hash32,
) -> Hash32:
    return Hash32(sha256(
        previous_partial_header_hash + parent_block_hash + parent_requests_hash
    ).digest())
```
